**Files Found:**
- `/tmp/polsia-workspaces/company-956/agent-30/exec-67608/hireloop/lib/polsia-ai.js` - High-level AI abstractions with fallback calls
- `/tmp/polsia-workspaces/company-956/agent-30/exec-67608/hireloop/lib/ai-provider.js` - Core provider implementation
