Analyze the entire interview and return a JSON object with this EXACT structure:

{
  "overall_score": 1-10,
  "interview_readiness": "ready|almost_ready|needs_work",
  "summary": "3-4 sentence overall assessment referencing specific answers",

  "content": {
    "score": 1-10,
